fields.bio: I love to read, swim, and code! I also like to write when I have free time.
I love reading classic novels, web development, and shopping! Let's have a girls day.
Hi, my name is Mike. I like coffee, programming, and video games. I also like learning new things so I am always reading. If you are looking for me, you are sure to find me near a computer.
Hi my name is Josh, although I am also called Joshy. I like to make puns, play video games, and hangout with friends. I like to thing I am stylish, everyone else tells me I am.

I am a very weird person that likes to have fun with friends. :) Even though I'm weird, all my friends love me for who I am. I'm very much into writing and hope to become a famous writer someday. :) 

I love dogs! I love to read. I can't live without music, it's pretty much my life. I listen to music at least 24/7. :)
